column1: SELECT   f.year_key *100 + f.month_key AS maand,   m.month_name ||  ' ' || f.year_key AS maand_naam,  SUM( f.m_budgetbedrag ) * -1 AS begroting,   SUM( f.m_realisatiebedrag ) * -1 AS realisatie  FROM fact_exploitatie AS f  INNER JOIN month_names AS m ON f.month_key = m.month  INNER JOIN dim_grootboek AS g ON f.grootboek_key = g.grootboek_key  INNER JOIN closure_organisatie AS c ON f.organisatie_key = c.organisatie_key AND c.parent = 752  WHERE f.tenant_key = %TENANT_ID%  AND g.gb_verdichting_code_1 IN ( 3, 4, 5 )   AND f.year_key = 2012  AND f.month_key >= 06  AND f.month_key <= 11  GROUP BY maand, maand_naam  ORDER BY maand, maand_naam;
